<template>

        <v-divider></v-divider>

        <v-list nav>

          >
            <v-list-item-content>
              <v-list-item-title>{{ navList.name }}</v-list-item-title>
            </v-list-item-content>
          </v-list-item>
        </v-list>
      </v-container>

            style="text-transform: none"
            to="/raspios"

          <v-tab

            to="/nginx"

    <v-footer color="deep-purple darken-4" dark app>
      <v-row justify=end>
        <v-card color="deep-purple darken-4" flat>
          written by g.oishi
        </v-card>
      </v-row>
    </v-footer>
  </v-app>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  computed: {
    drawer () {
      return this.$store.getters.drawer
    },
    navLists () {
      return this.$store.getters.navLists
    }
  }
}
</script>
